Reasoning: The paper deals with vision-based depth reconstruction, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The application of this technique to mobile robotics (vSLAM) suggests that it could also fall under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of fully-convolutional neural networks (FCNNs) indicates that the paper could also be classified under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the fact that the paper presents experimental results and evaluates the suggested models suggests that it could also be classified under computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CVPR).
